sub_title: Data Processor at Deep BV, Hydrography & Geophysics
summary:
I spend my time checking out bottoms.

Sea, river, lake and canal bottoms that is. Also, the occasional beach.

Processing hydrographic and geophysical data, from multibeam to mag, its all my bag. 

Experience with: BeamworX, QGIS, Oasis Montaj, Qinsy, Terramodel and BrisCAD. 
NT2 - A2 Level in Dutch. Currently tackling B1.
